{"tid":258514,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"日日返到屋企見老婆扮死 佢想點","createTime":"2017-05-26T07:49:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-26T09:29:58.000Z","uid":79471,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a67ae2a67e8227a4b7dddb543bfecaf86412f8f1","tid":258514,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T07:49:04.000Z","msg":"返到屋企老婆一定扮死<br />\n<br />\n到底係咩事？<br />\n<br />\n返到屋企一開門就見到老婆瞓底係地上<br />\n<br />\n一開始我嚇撚死我，但因為之後每天都係噉<br />\n<br />\n所以我咆哮「快啲起身！」噉就算<br />\n<br />\n於是第二天變咗口吐鮮血<br />\n<br />\n一星期之後變咗做血染白T恤。<br />\n<br />\n最近係唔係無新花樣呢？<br />\n<br />\n定係話山窮水盡思維暴走？<br />\n<br />\n老婆有時把箭插喺太陽穴<br />\n<br />\n有時把膠袋套喺頭上。（由於呼吸，個袋會猛烈膨脹收縮）<br />\n<br />\n噚日仲穿着軍裝抱住支步槍一副為榮譽壯烈犧牲嘅樣子<br />\n<br />\n當然，我腳步無停，從老婆身邊無視行過<br />\n<br />\n佢到底希望我點做？<br />\n<br />\n仲有佢將來到底想做咩？<br />\n<br />\n我完全冇頭緒，有冇巴打可以話比我聽？<br />\n<br />\n哩幾天，佢保持住頭畀弓箭貫穿嘅狀態整晚餐"},{"pid":"4959fba85eae97491f2314318b9a76f9cb981b37","tid":258514,"uid":58914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T07:51:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"210f67acf86f9de42c4bd82a3bc5dd821c39085d","tid":258514,"uid":14440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T07:52:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">btw首歌好撚sweet</span>"},{"pid":"8aeaf33419d27e08aa58d14666de0468926b2d67","tid":258514,"uid":81463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T07:52:12.000Z","msg":"你老婆係榮倉奈奈?"},{"pid":"180a1019e4c8b5bc8a52dd5c2b6bd2458ccb21bc","tid":258514,"uid":46608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T07:54:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5745157b62478efaddc6ec105b63bfc43a7ddbd0","tid":258514,"uid":40839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T07:55:17.000Z","msg":"首歌幾好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5f381f50066ceb39a0e4d3d7619f2ecfeb531e9","tid":258514,"uid":75694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T07:55:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec602da440b35f706c86df92cc433c0f2fcf9b44","tid":258514,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T07:56:05.000Z","msg":"潮文 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cb017f66b8ccd46b7e5d4db1d6f54337daae6a9","tid":258514,"uid":1918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T07:56:15.000Z","msg":"拍左電影啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9f221f3e4296b778938c7fc21ca6f1540a13046","tid":258514,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T08:01:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拍左電影啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n鱷魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"260c3eae8dbdc7fbf393a654c76857d1c51d735f","tid":258514,"uid":54639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T08:03:04.000Z","msg":"前前前世？"},{"pid":"9a84f5f252d5b9a08bf7c6662f6a15d41099919e","tid":258514,"uid":40839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T08:10:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前前前世？</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/N1OcR0ZnuAY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FN1OcR0ZnuAY&d=ugRGr0K6dq0P6yXV8xHYtP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=aff0f523\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/N1OcR0ZnuAY</a>"},{"pid":"d54bb319ec06cc249cf787d644fc485d666e0825","tid":258514,"uid":54639,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T09:15:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>前前前世？</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/N1OcR0ZnuAY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu